ng-qu%C3%A2n-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o/poem-dwsKivXoJ5TA_Qil5ceCng">Tòng quân khẩu hào - 從軍口號</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Tr%E1%BB%ABng-Chi/author-V8R7nhhotOVWLkm8vPg4Jg">Tiền Trừng Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%E1%BB%A5c-ph%C3%A1n-quan-s%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%A2y-phi%C3%AAn/poem-Eln7UzT_jIi6xc1ZwNyliA">Tống Dương lục phán quan sứ tây phiên - 送楊六判官使西蕃</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tokugawa-Mitsukuni/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0/poem-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Trường tương tư - 長相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tokugawa-Mitsukuni/author-wy3Pfe_yc9Hmd6DdVbKQfQ">Tokugawa Mitsukuni</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/V%C4%83n-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%C3%A2n-b%E1%BB%A9c-th%E1%BB%A7-V%C4%A9nh-An-H%C3%A0-tam-t%E1%BB%89nh-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-dS4OgyPwnu3cdUXdInCBsw">Văn dương nhân bức thủ Vĩnh An Hà tam tỉnh cảm tác - 聞洋人逼取永安河三省感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/author-GaA0SgEPvCmkAgLupJfzCQ">Trần Bích San</a>)<br></div>	</div>
